# 🚀 Day 76/90 – Store Multiple Blood Reports and Display Them

Congratulations! 🎉

On **Day 75**, your Flutter app **sent** data to FastAPI using a **POST** request.

Today, you'll make the backend **remember** the submitted reports (while it's running) and allow Flutter to retrieve and display all of them.

> **Note:** This is an in-memory list. If you stop the backend, the data will be cleared. On Day 77 we'll replace this with a real database.

